WEBVTT

00:01.840 --> 00:03.600
The will was sent back to the capital

00:04.280 --> 00:05.840
Wang Ming was ordered to assist in governance

00:06.240 --> 00:08.560
Crown Prince Sikong Sheng successfully ascended the throne

00:08.880 --> 00:11.280
And changed the era name to Taian the following year

00:11.760 --> 00:13.960
Posthumously titled the late Emperor Sikong Yao as Wu

00:14.160 --> 00:16.120
Historically known as Emperor Xuanwu

00:16.960 --> 00:18.000
The second year of Taian

00:18.280 --> 00:20.000
Sikong Sheng moved the capital to Yong'an

00:20.160 --> 00:22.840
Fulfilled the long-cherished wish to return to the old capital

00:23.840 --> 00:24.560
The same year

00:25.120 --> 00:28.000
Sikong Sheng enfeoffed Sikong Xu as Prince of Yan

00:28.360 --> 00:30.480
Giving him the responsibility to expand territory

00:30.720 --> 00:32.840
While he himself governed the court

00:33.000 --> 00:34.080
Focusing on governance

00:35.000 --> 00:36.480
Sikong Sheng once joked

00:36.800 --> 00:39.160
War by the Prince of Yan, governance by me

00:39.720 --> 00:41.000
The two worked together

00:41.280 --> 00:44.720
Becoming a timeless tale

00:48.160 --> 00:48.920
Come, Yu'er

00:54.800 --> 00:56.120
Your Majesty, coming, coming

00:58.280 --> 00:59.880
Your Majesty

01:01.480 --> 01:04.040
Your Majesty, your younger brother has not failed the mission

01:04.920 --> 01:05.720
You rascal

01:06.560 --> 01:08.400
These years Xunyang has been in Yan Dong

01:08.840 --> 01:10.160
Second brother was afraid they'd bully you

01:12.160 --> 01:13.920
Fortunately, Murong of Yan Dong knows his place

01:14.440 --> 01:16.480
These years he's been respectfully serving little sister

01:17.520 --> 01:20.160
Your Majesty said to find an opportunity to put him in his place

01:20.960 --> 01:23.800
Your younger brother, it's hard to hit a smiling face

01:24.360 --> 01:25.560
Alright, let's go

01:25.920 --> 01:26.640
Rare reunion

01:27.200 --> 01:27.920
First tell Father

01:28.400 --> 01:29.200
That we've brought Xunyang back

01:29.880 --> 01:30.200
Let's go

01:52.760 --> 01:54.440
During Sikong Sheng's reign

01:54.760 --> 01:56.640
Xuan Kingdom reached its peak

01:56.840 --> 01:58.160
All lands submitted

01:58.400 --> 01:59.840
Received tribute from all nations

02:00.440 --> 02:02.840
Border peoples requested to join

02:03.440 --> 02:05.640
Honoring Sikong Sheng as Heavenly King

02:05.960 --> 02:08.960
Historically known as the Taian Golden Age
